Primary bedroom is located downstairs with a walk-in closet and private bath. Half bath is located in the laundry room. Large level yard with a fenced in backyard. Large bedrooms with extra closets. HVAC Nov 2017. Fresh paint downstairs. New Stainless Steel Refrigerator, Microwave, & Stove/Oven.
